snippet.title: Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu 2009 (PS2) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
A full game of Jikkyou Poweful Pro Yakyuu 2009, the final PS2 game in Konami's Pawapuro series. The previous game in the series was Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu 15, so this also represented a break in the series' naming scheme. 

Hiroshima Carp vs. Chunichi Dragons at the seaside lighthouse park.
